body: Hi everybody ,  hope you are well , I updated LB & HB  but unfortunately, Hb can't recognize Openstudio , it's asking to install the latest version . the latest version of openstudio 1.12 is compatible with energyplus 8.5 but for HB we need energyplus 8.4 , so I installed openstudio 1.10 which is compatible with energy plus 8.4  but I have the same problem.
